code: public static Environment parseUnmodified(String fileName) throws IOException {     final URL url = EnvironmentFileUtil.class.getClassLoader().getResource(fileName).     Objects.requireNonNull(url).     return Environment.parse(url). }

public static Environment parseModified(String fileName, Map<String, String> replaceVars) throws IOException {     final URL url = EnvironmentFileUtil.class.getClassLoader().getResource(fileName).     Objects.requireNonNull(url).     String schema = FileUtils.readFileUtf8(new File(url.getFile())).     for (Map.Entry<String, String> replaceVar : replaceVars.entrySet()) {         schema = schema.replace(replaceVar.getKey(), replaceVar.getValue()).     }     return Environment.parse(schema). }
